Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban ƙasar Donald Trump ya soma taron da yamma a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia.
Yana ɗaya daga cikin tarurrukan Trump biyar na mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tarurruka na dindindin kamar su a jihar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka dakatar da zaben da aka yi na zabar wanda ya zaɓa a matsayin alƙali a Kotun Koli, Trump ya yi niyyar gayyatar mutane zuwa zaɓen tsakiyar mulkinsa yayin da jam'iyyarsa ta Republican ke cikin haɗari na karɓan iko a majalisa a zaɓen Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron zai faru, kuma yaya za ka iya yin hakan a Intane?
Wannan taron Trump ne da misalin karfe 7 na yammacin rana, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon taron a Intane ta hanyar dandalin Intane na YouTube.
Trump ya kamata ya yi magana a kan shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh da aka zaɓa a kotun koli, wanda ya jawo fushi domin yana da alaƙa da zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh na yin fyade yayin da aka dakatar da kuri'un tabbatar da shi na mako guda yanzu yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma, babban manufar taron ne don a samu nasara a zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, an ba da rahoton cewa, manufar taron Trump guda biyar "ta kasance don ƙarfafa masu goyon bayanta da kuma masu son jin daɗin al'umma yayin da Jam'iyyar Republican ke neman kāre da kuma ƙara yawan 'yan majalisar ta", in ji jaridar Reuters.
"Sakamakon da aka samu na yin wannan taron shi ne cewa shugabanni suna da iko a kan wannan taron a wurare da yawa a lokacin da ake gudanar da taron", in ji wani shugaban da ya yi wa Trump zaben, wanda bai so a ambaci sunansa ba, a wani jawabi da aka ba jaridar Reuters.
Za a gayyaci masu sauraron taron daga Ohio da Pennsylvania zuwa filin wasa na Wesbanco a garin Wheeling kuma za a yi watsa shirye-shiryen rediyo na Pittsburgh", in ji wani jaridar West Virginia Metro.
A ranar Asabar ne na biyu a watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci yammacin Virginia, birni da ya lashe kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, wanda shi ma jam'iyyar Republican ce a West Virginia.
"Ƙarfafawa da shugabanni suka yi a wannan zaɓen ba ya ba Morrisey kyakkyawan labari", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar rahotanni na Reuters.
Gasar Ryder ta shekara ta 2018: 'Yan wasan Amurka sun nuna cewa sun yi nasara a wasanni don ci gaba da samun damar yin wasa a ranar Lahadi
Bayan an buga wasanni uku, wasan Asabar na mutane huɗu zai zama wasan da ya cancanci gasar Ryder.
Aikin da ake yi a wasanni ba shi da sauƙi, amma a gasa kamar wannan, 'yan wasa suna da tabbaci sosai.
Su waye ne za su sami wannan gatan?
"Sun ci gaba da maki shida amma yanzu suna da maki huɗu kawai, don haka muna ɗaukan wannan a matsayin dama", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake tafiya a hankali.
Ƙungiyar Turai tana da damar yin nasara, tana da maki 4 a gabanta a wasanni 12.
Spieth ya ce, 'yan wasan Amirka suna ganin cewa suna da abubuwa da yawa da za su ƙarfafa su, kamar yadda Spieth da Justin Thomas suka yi a ranar da suka yi wasa tare kuma suka samu maki uku daga cikin maki huɗu.
Spieth ya yi nasara kuma ya kafa misali mai kyau.
Sa'ad da shi da Thomas suka ci gaba da yin ihu, sai aka ji yadda 'yan wasan suka jefa ƙwallon a cikin rami, kuma hakan ya sa ƙungiyoyin suka sami maki huɗu a kan huɗu.
Da ya jefa kwallon a rami, ya ci wasan a rami na 15, kuma mutane suka yi girma kamar yadda ya yi, abin da ya nuna cewa ya gaskata cewa tawagar Amirka ba ta ci nasara ba.
Spieth ya ce: "Dole ne mutum ya saka tufafi masu kyau kuma ya yi tunani game da wasannin da yake yi.
Wannan shi ne abin da dukan 'yan wasan suke da shi a nan.
Bayan ramuka 18 kawai, ƙungiyar ta nuna wani mutum.
'Yan wasan da suka ci Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu sune Frascesco Milinari da Tommy Fleetwood, wadanda a halin yanzu su ne masu cin nasara a gasar Ryder.
Waɗannan 'yan wasan Turai biyu da ake so sun samu maki huɗu a cikin huɗu kuma ba za su yi kuskure ba.
"Moliwood" ne kawai 'yan wasan biyu da ba su buga ƙwallon ƙafa a kusa da rami a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, da kuma ranar Asabar da safe, Jumma'a da rana da kuma ramin tara na ƙarshe.
Wannan, da kuma ƙarfin da suke da shi da kuma yadda suke yin wasan motsa jiki sun nuna cewa su 'yan wasa ne da za su yi fama da rashin nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani ɗan wasan da zai iya cin nasarar da ya fi na Fleetwood ko Molinari na Turai a lokacin da rana ta faɗi a Le Golf National.
Wataƙila suna cikin koguna dabam dabam.
Har ila yau, yana da sauƙi a ce ƙungiyar Turai ta ci kofin.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi nasara a kan Sergio Garcia, wanda ya yi aiki tare da Alex Noren a wasan ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu da safe.
A lokacin da suka jefa ƙwallon a rami da ke kusa da su kuma suka jefa ƙwallon sau biyu a ramin farko na tara, sun ci gaba da yin nasara a ƙungiyarsu kuma sun ƙi su dawo.
Amma babu abin da zai rage nasara ga Allah.
Wasan da ake buga da mutane huɗu yana da ban sha'awa sosai domin tattaunawa da ake yi da mutane biyu a kowane rukuni, da kuma yadda ake ba da shawara da kuma yadda ake canja tsarin wasan.
A yanzu, 'yan wasan Turai sun yi nasara sosai a wasan kuma suna zuwa wasan karshe suna da kyakkyawan jagora, amma wasan da 'yan wasan nan huɗu suka yi ya nuna cewa 'yan wasan Amirka suna da damar yin nasara, musamman ma 'yan wasan Amirka.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta ci gaba da ci da maki 10 zuwa 6 a ranar ƙarshe ta gasar Ryder
Ƙungiyar Turai za ta yi nasara sosai a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder bayan ta ci ta Amirka a wasanni huɗu na kwallon kafa a ranar Asabar da maki 10-6.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci wani rukuni da ke fama da Tiger Woods, kuma nasarar da suka samu a wasan da aka yi a filin wasa na Le Golf National ta kai su matsayi na huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai da Thomas Bjorn ya koyar, suna neman su sake lashe kofin da suka ƙi su kare shekaru biyu da suka shige a filin wasa na Hazeltine, sun ci gaba da buga wa Amirkawa wasan su na safe na ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu, a kan jadawalin wasa 3-1.
Ƙungiyar Amirka ta ci nasara a wasanni biyu, amma ba ta hana ta yin nasara ba.
A ranar Lahadi, ana bukatar maki takwas a wasanni 12 da aka buga don a lashe kofin.
Fleetwood ne ɗan wasan Turai na farko da ya samu maki huɗu a jere a gasar, kuma ta hanyar wasan da suka yi a ƙarshen Asabar, shi da Molinari ne 'yan wasan da ake kira "Molliwood" da kuma 'yan wasan biyu da suka samu maki huɗu a wasanni huɗu na farko a tarihin gasar Ryder.
Bayan da suka ci Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu, sun ci Woods da Bryson Dechambeau, ɗan wasan farko a gasar Amirka, da maki 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi ƙoƙari ya yi nasara a wasanni biyu na Asabar, ya nuna rashin nasara a wasanni 19 na wasanni 29 na wasanni hudu da hudu da kuma wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda aka yi watsi da shi a wasan da aka yi da safe na ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu, ya kafa ƙungiya ta biyu tare da Henrik Stenson a wasan da aka yi da huɗu kuma ya ci nasara da maki 2 da 1 a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - na uku a duniya.
A wannan rana mai sanyi a kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris, ƙungiyar Turai ba ta wuce ta tsakiya ba.
Jordan Spieth wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku tare da Justin Thomas ya jagoranci tawagar Amurka da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci gaba da yin nasara da maki 2 da 1 a kan Jon-Rahm da Ian Poulter na tawagar Spain a gasar ƙwallon ƙafa ta hudu kuma sun ci Poulter da rory Mcllroy 4 da 3 a gasar ƙwallon ƙafa ta uku duk da cewa sun yi rashin nasara a wasanni biyu na farko.
A tarihin gasar Ryder ne kawai sau biyu da ƙungiyar da ta rage maki huɗu a wasan da ta yi, ta ci nasara, ko da yake Furyk da ke kare kofin tana bukatar ta daidaita da sauran ƙungiyoyi don ta ci kofin.
Bayan sun yi nasara a matsayin na biyu a cikin kwanaki biyu, wasan da aka yi a ranar Lahadi zai zama da wuya.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce 'babu abin da zai sa ta daina yin amfani da makamai ba tare da amincewa ba
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ci gaba da nuna rashin amincewa da gwamnatin Amirka ya ƙara ƙaruwa kuma ba a bukatar ƙasar ta daina amfani da makaman nukiliya a lokacin ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya yi jawabi a taron shekara-shekara na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta yi "aikin da ya nuna ta yi nasara" a shekarar da ta shige kamar su daina gwada makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, ta rushe wani makaman nukiliya da kuma alkawarin da ta yi cewa ba za ta ƙara yin amfani da makaman nukiliya ba.
Ya ce: "Amma ba mu taɓa ganin Amirka ta sake yin irin wannan aikin ba.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amirka ba, ba za mu iya kasancewa da kwanciyar hankali ba kuma ba za mu iya daina amfani da makaman nukiliya ba".
Ko da yake Ri ya maimaita korafin da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi game da ƙin amfani da makaman nukiliya "a hankali" ga Amirka, wadda ta cancanci a yaba wa Koriya ta Arewa domin ta yi nasara a wannan batun, ya yi magana da ƙarfi domin ba ta ƙyale ta ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a dā.
Ri ya yi maganar saƙon da Kim Jong Un da Trump suka rubuta a taron farko na shugaban Amurka da Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin gwada "ƙarancin amfani da makaman nukiliya a tsibirin Koriya" kuma Trump ya jaddada batun tsaro a Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi ƙoƙari ta kawo ƙarshen yaƙin tsakanin Koriya ta Arewa da Koriya ta Kudu, amma Amirka ta ce ta daina amfani da makaman nukiliya.
Amirka ta ƙi ta rage yawan hukuncin da ake yi wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Ri ya ce: "Amurka tana ta dagewa ga "karin amfani da makaman nukiliya" kuma tana ƙara sauƙaƙa ayyukan da ta yi wa Koriya ta Arewa don ta tilasta wa Koriya ta Arewa, kuma Amirka ta ƙi "ta sanar da cewa an daina yin yaƙi", in ji Ri.
