HIV da AIDS: Kasar Sin ta ce yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar ya ƙaru da kashi 14 cikin 100
Ƙasar ta sanar da cewa adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya ƙaru da kashi 14 cikin ɗari.
Mutane 820,000 da suka kamu da cutar a ƙasar, in ji masana kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kashi na huɗu na shekara ta 2018 ne kawai, mutane 40,000 ne suka halarci taron.
Yawancin mutane sun kamu da cutar ta hanyar jima'i kuma hakan ya haifar da canji.
Da farko, ana samun kamuwa da cutar ta HIV ta hanyar jini.
Amma, an rage yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar wannan hanyar, in ji wani jami'in kiwon lafiya na ƙasar Sin a wani taro a Yunnan.
A kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Ana samun kamuwa da cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i a yawancin mutane da suke yin jima'i da maza ko mata.
An soke dokar hana 'yan luwadi a ƙasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma ana nuna wariya ga masu aikata lalata a ƙasar.
Domin halin da ake ciki a duniya, an ce kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna aure.
Ana samun wannan cuta ta hanyar jima'i da ba a kāre shi ba.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin Sin ta yi alkawarin ba da taimako ga kowa don ya magance cutar.
