An samu wannan sakon a dandalin Capitol Hill a ranar Alhamis bayan wani da ba a san shi ba ya wallafa shi a lokacin da ake zargin cewa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zaɓa ya zama alƙali a Kotun Koli, yana ƙoƙarin yin fyade da mata.
An sanar da wannan saƙon bayan da 'yan majalisar uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo na jam'iyyar Conservative kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun kuma bayyana cewa an haɗa adireshin IP ɗin da ke ba da bayanin asalin wurin zuwa ofishin Waters" kuma sun ba da ƙarin bayani game da ma'aikacin Waters, in ji Hill.
Waters ya ce: "Wannan labarin banza ƙarya ce.
"Ma'aikatan ofishina - wanda aka ambata sunansa kuma an saka asirinsa da kuma amincinsa a kan gungumen azaba domin labarin ƙarya - ba shi ne ya ba da wannan saƙon ba.
Wannan labarin banza ƙarya ce".
Wasu mutane da yawa a Intane sun yi ta sukar abin da Waters ya faɗa, har da tsohon sakataren fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer ya rubuta: "Rashin yarda yana nuna fushi.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da ikon zama Majalisar Dokoki.
Idan aka yi wa wani ƙarya, bai kamata ya yi fushi ba.
Kada su yi banza da iko.
Kada su yi ƙiyayya da maƙasudin waɗanda suke yi musu ƙarya.
Ya kamata su kasance da natsuwa da kuma kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya yi magana game da jawabin Waters da kuma yadda aka tsauta wa alƙalai, Kavanaugh da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat, waɗanda aka zarge da yin fushi a lokacin sauraron shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, mai wakiltar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman a cire Waters daga zaben tsakiyar mulkinsa ya yi magana a shafin Twitter.
"Babban labari ne, idan gaskiya ne", in ji ta a shafinta na Twitter.
A jawabinsa, Waters ya ce ofishin ya sanar da "masu-aiki da kuma 'yan sanda game da batun.
Ya ci gaba da cewa: "Za mu tabbatar da cewa an san masu wallafa wannan labarin kuma za a tuhume su bisa ga doka domin suna da haɗari da kuma ɓata wa ma'aikatan ofishina rai".
An yi wa wasan kwaikwayon Johnny English Strikes Again ado - Barkwanci na Atkinson
A yau, ana yin amfani da fim din da aka yi a jaridar Burtaniya don ya nuna cewa Birtaniya ta bar Tarayyar Turai, kuma ana yin hakan a wani fim mai suna Jonny English - wanda aka fara a shekara ta 2003 da fim din Jonny English kuma aka sake yin fim din a shekara ta 2011 da aka sake yin fim din Jonny English Reborn.
Yin magana ba da ladabi da kuma baƙar magana game da wannan batun zai nuna cewa yin duniya a matsayin kasuwanci ba daidai ba ne?
A kowane hali, Johnny English mai ido mai girma da kuma bayyanar da ba ta da kyau ya kasance da ƙwarewar sake yin abubuwa a sau biyu  don ya nuna cewa yana da ikon yin fim mai ban dariya da ba a Turanci ba wanda zai kai ga mutane da yawa.
Wannan mutumin mai ban sha'awa ne, wanda yake yin ba'a kamar shi ne 'yan sanda, kuma Bean, kuma babban mutum ne na Burtaniya kamar saƙon Chariots of Fire a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta 2012 a London.
Wannan labarin ya fito ne daga ziyarar Atkinson a wani tsohon fim na rediyo na Barclay, wanda ya jawo tashin hankali.
Akwai wurare masu ban sha'awa na wata ko biyu a cikin sabon fim ɗin Johnny English.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da Johnny English ya bi jirgin sama yana da riguna da kuma wuka a kan kwalkwali.
An ga yadda Atkinson yake yin wasan kwaikwayo, amma baƙonsa yana da ban dariya kuma yana da "ƙawa" musamman idan aka lura da yadda 007 da Mission Impossible suke da ban dariya.
Ba'a yi wa yarinyar ba, amma ga manya ne, kuma a ganina, Johnny English ba ya nuna basira da kuma kwanciyar hankali fiye da Atkinson da yake nunawa a fim.
Wannan labarin ya nuna cewa ƙasar Britaniya tana cikin matsala.
Wasu masu amfani da kwamfuta sun shiga cikin kwamfutocin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizo na 'yan leƙen asiri na ƙasar Birtaniya, kuma sun ɓoye saƙonnin da aka samu daga dukan jami'an gwamnati na ƙasar, wanda ya sa wani jami'in gwamnati a wani yanki ya damu - wani ɓangare na aikin Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya faru na firaministan da ke jin tsoro da kuma wahala, wanda ke fuskantar matsaloli a matsayinsa na baƙon siyasa: Emma Thompson tana yin ƙyama a kan abin da ta ɗauka a matsayin mai neman aure kamar Teresa May amma a wasan kwaikwayo babu abin da za a ƙara.
Masu ba shi shawara sun gaya masa cewa tun da yake kowane ɗan leƙen asiri yana da matsala, ya kamata ya kori wani daga aikinsa.
Wannan ya shafi Johnny English, wani babban malamin makarantar sakandare, wanda yake koyar da aikin da jami'in gwamnati yake yi a ɓoye: popes suna da abubuwa masu kyau, yayin da English ke koyar da yara dabam-dabam game da leken asiri.
An kai English ba zato ba tsammani zuwa wani taro a Whitehall don a yi masa saƙon gaggawa, kuma a wurin ya haɗu da wani ɗan'uwa mai suna Bough, wanda ya daɗe yana aiki tare da shi, wanda Ben Miller ya halarci taron.
Yanzu Bough ya yi aure, ya auri wani shugaban rundunar jiragen ruwa, wani ɗan wasan da aka yi wa Vicki Pepperdine rashin amfani.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin, masu yin aikin soja na Sarki mai girma sun yi aiki da ba daidai ba, suna haɗuwa da 'yar Olga Kurylenko, Ophelia Bulletova mai ba da tasiri.
Yanzu haka, firaministan ya damu da wani mai arziki da ya ce zai iya magance matsalar kwamfuta a ƙasar Britaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya ɗauke.
English da Bough sun soma aikin: sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa da alama suna ba da abinci; hakan ya sa aka yi ta yin tawaye har suka shiga jirgin ƙasa mai tsayi na Volta; kuma English sun yi ta yin tawaye sa'ad da suke son su yi amfani da na'urar sauraron sauti don su bincika abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Duk abin da ya faru a ƙarshen wannan sashen ya faru, amma yadda yake da ban sha'awa da kuma ban tsoro, ya nuna cewa fim ne na yara a ko'ina.
Wannan abu ne mai ban sha'awa.
Kamar sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, na yi kasawa wajen tunani: shin masu fim na Burtaniya ba za su ba Rowan Atinkson wani ɓangare na aikinsa ba?
Jam'iyyar Labor ta ƙi amincewa da tsarin da ya ce 'yan ƙasar Britaniya su yi aiki na kwana huɗu a mako amma a biya su kwanaki biyar
Jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta yi babban ƙuduri game da ganin 'yan ƙasar Burtaniya su yi aiki kwana huɗu a mako - amma su biya kwanaki biyar.
Ƙungiyar ta ce tana son ma'aikata su ba ma'aikatansu kuɗin da suka samu ta wajen amfani da fasaha ta zamani ta wajen ba su hutu.
Wannan tsarin zai ba ma'aikata hutu na kwana uku - amma suna samun albashin da ya dace.
Bisa ga bayanan da aka fitar, wannan ra'ayin zai iya "saduwa" da ra'ayin tattalin arziki na jam'iyyar da kuma ra'ayin sauya duniya don amfanin ma'aikata.
Hukumar ta amince da sauya tsarin aiki na kwana huɗu a mako a matsayin hanya don ma'aikata su amfana daga ci gaban fasaha.
Wani shugaban jam'iyyar Labor ya gaya wa jaridar The Sunday Times: 'Ana sa ran a sanar da sake duba tsarin a cikin shekara guda.
'Ba za a iya yin aiki a rana ɗaya ba amma tsarin aiki na kwana huɗu a mako ya dace da manufofin jam'iyyar domin ma'aikata su amfana daga ci gaban tattalin arziki da kuma sababbin hanyoyin kasuwanci.'
Jam'iyyar Labor ba ta fara tabbatar da irin wannan shawarar ba, yayin da Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwanaki hudu a mako a lokacin zaben 2017.
Amma, ba dukan 'yan jam'iyyar Labor ba ne suke da wannan ra'ayin.
Wani mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Ba a yi amfani da ranar Asabar na kwana huɗu a matsayin manufofin jam'iyyar ba kuma ba a yi amfani da ita ba".
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da damar taron Labor Party a makon da ya gabata don gabatar da shawararsa game da yadda jama'a za su amfana daga tattalin arzikin ƙasa.
McDonnell ya ce ya ƙuduri aniya ya karɓi iko daga 'masu-mulki marasa bege' da kuma 'masu-riba' na kamfanonin agaji.
Manufofin shugaban kuma suna nufin cewa masu hannun jari a masana'antar ruwa ba za su iya dawo da kudaden su ba kamar yadda gwamnatin Labor za ta iya 'karɓar' wasu kudaden don dalilai da suka ga ba daidai ba.
Ya kuma amince da tsarin da zai sa ma'aikata su yi rajista na kashi 10, wanda zai sa ma'aikata su samu albashin da ya kai fam 500 a shekara.
Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy ya gaya wa "60 Minutes" ko binciken FBI a kan batun Kavanaugh zai iya canja ra'ayinsu
Binciken FBI game da zargin da aka yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta zaben karshe na zabensa a Kotun Koli da kusan mako guda, yana haifar da tambaya ko sakamakon binciken da ofishin ya samu ya kamata ya canza kowane sanatan Republican don kada ya goyi bayan shi.
A wata hira da aka watsa a ranar Lahadi, mai gabatar da labarai na gidan talabijin na "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi Sanatocin Jam'iyyar Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI za ta iya samun wani abu da zai sa su canza ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya yi magana a fili fiye da abokinsa na Carolina ta Kudu.
"A gaskiya, wannan shi ne", in ji Kennedy.
"Ina zuwa sauraron shari'ar, na ce, na yi magana da Alƙali Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan wannan, kuma ya ce, 'Ka yi haka?'
Ya kasance da gaba gaɗi, ya ƙuduri aniya, kuma ya kasance da tabbaci".
Amma, ba a taɓa yin amfani da kuri'ar Graham ba.
Ya ce: "Ba na canja ra'ayina game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma dole ne in canja idan ba a yi wani babban laifi ba".
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan kawai: Brett ya ƙi shi sosai, "in ji Graham, yana magana game da Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma ba wanda ya ambata shi ya tabbatar da hakan.
Wannan labarin ya faru shekaru 36 da suka shige.
Ba na ganin wani abu da zai canja a yanzu".
Menene Bikin Kiɗa na Ƙasashen Duniya, kuma yaya wannan bikin ya rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar da ta zo, birnin New York ne za su yi bikin, wanda ake yi kowace shekara kuma masu kida da yawa za su rera waƙa don su kawar da talauci a dukan duniya.
A wannan shekara, za a yi bikin shekaru bakwai a jere, kuma dubban mutane za su yi ta zuwa wurin wurin shakatawa na Central Park don su yi farin ciki da mawaƙa kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B, da Shawn Mendes da kuma sanar da jama'a cewa ainihin manufar bikin ita ce kawar da talauci a shekara ta 2030.
Wannan bikin na 'Yan Waƙar Duniya da aka soma a shekara ta 2012 wani ɓangare ne na shirin Global Poverty Project, wanda ke taimakawa wajen kawar da talauci a dukan duniya ta wajen ƙara yawan mutanen da ke fama da talauci.
Don a samu tikitin shiga (sai dai idan kana son ka sayi tikitin wani mutum mai daraja) masu halartar taron suna bukatar su yi ayyuka dabam-dabam kamar su ba da kai, aika wasiƙa ta Intane ga shugaban ƙasa, yin baftisma ko kuma yin wani abu mai kyau da zai taimaka wajen yaɗa manufar kawar da talauci.
Amma, yaya wannan bikin ya cika shekaru 12 da suka rage?
Shin yin amfani da dandalin yin waƙoƙi kyauta yana da kyau ko kuma yin yaƙi a Intane - ana ganin cewa yin sa hannu a takardar shaidar ko aika saƙo a Intane ne kawai yake da muhimmanci?
Tun daga shekara ta 2011, an ce an samu abubuwa miliyan 19 daga masu sauraron wannan bikin.
Sun ce wannan ya taimaka wa shugabannin ƙasashe su tsai da shawara kuma su tsara shirin saka hannun jari na dala biliyan 37 don su kula da mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon shekara ta 2018, ƙungiyar ta ba da jerin abubuwan da aka tsara na 390 daga abubuwan da suka faru, wanda aka ba da ko kuma an riga an tattara dala biliyan 10.
A sakamakon haka, an canja rayuwar mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin ayyukan da aka yi sun haɗa da inganta lafiyar yara, wanda ya fito ne daga wata ƙungiya ta Birtaniya da ke "tallafa wa yara zuwa ga iyakarsu", wadda ta yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga ƙasar Rwanda don magance cutar ta lalata yara, bayan da ta samu saƙonni 4,700 a shafin Twitter.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu son jin dadi, gwamnatocin ƙasashe, da kuma mutane kamar ku, za mu iya kawar da rashin jin daɗi ɗaya daga cikin masu ba da shawara kan kiwon lafiya, Tracey Ullman ya gaya wa ƙungiyar masu sauraron kiɗa a birnin London a watan Afrilu na shekara ta 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce ta hanyar jawabai sama da 5000 an ƙarfafa kungiyar ta karfafa gwamnatin Burtaniya don inganta lafiyar mata da yara, kuma gwamnatin ta ba da sanarwar ba da tallafin kuɗi ga shirin wanda zai taimaka wa mata da yara miliyan 5.
A amsar tambayar da aka yi musu a dandalin Intane, Me kake gani za mu iya magance talauci?"
"Wannan yaƙi ne mai wuya da kuma daukan lokaci - kuma a wasu lokatai za mu yi sanyin gwiwa kuma mu kasa.
Amma, kamar ƙungiyoyin 'yanci da suka wanzu a dā, muna cim ma burinmu domin haɗin kai yana da ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, da Weeknd, da Shawn Mendes, da Cardi B, da Janelle Monáe suna cikin mawaƙa da za su yi bikin a birnin New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman suka shirya.
Amurka za ta iya amfani da sojoji don "hana" Rasha ta fitar da makamashi - Ministan Harkokin Wajen
Amurka za ta yi amfani da rundunar ta ta teku "idan ya cancanta" don hana fitar da duwatsu masu daraja da kuma makamashi daga Rasha zuwa ƙasashen waje, har da na Asiya, in ji Ministan Harkokin Wajen Amurka Ryan Zinke, a cewar rahoton Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya ce ayyukan da Rasha take yi a Siriya, inda ta yi aiki a ƙarƙashin umurnin gwamnati ta ƙasar - wata hanyar da za ta iya samun kuɗin da ake bukata don samun makamashin da ake bukata.
Ya ce: "Na yi imani cewa Rasha ta tura mutanenta zuwa Asiya don su sami kasuwa ta samar da makamashi kamar yadda ta yi a gabashin Turai.
Ya kuma ce akwai hanyoyin da za a magance wannan matsalar.
Ya ce: "Amurka tana da irin wannan damar, ta wajen amfani da rundunarmu ta jirgin ruwa, za mu iya buɗe ƙofofi kuma idan ya cancanta mu hana ƙarfinsu shiga kasuwa".
Zinke ya ce hakan ne a wani taron da ƙungiyar masu amfani da makamashi ta Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata ƙungiya da ba ta neman riba ba da ke kiran kanta "bakin masu amfani da makamashi" a Amirka.
Ya ce, zai zama kamar yadda Washington ta yi da Rasha, kuma hakan zai zama daidai da yadda ta yi da Iran.
"Hanyar da Rasha da Iran suke samu ta tattalin arziki, daidai take, ta ci gaba da bunkasa da kuma sauya man fetur", ya ce a lokacin da yake kwatanta Rasha da "abubuwan da ake amfani da su don samun riba" a kan man fetur.
Wannan ya faru ne a lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ta yi ƙoƙari ta ƙarfafa kasuwancin man fetur a Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha da ta fi ƙimar man fetur.
A wannan lokacin, shugabannin gwamnatin Trump da shugaban kasar Donald Trump, suna ƙoƙari su tilasta wa Jamus ta bar yarjejeniyar Nord Stream 2 da Rasha, Trump ya ce wannan shirin ya sa Jamus ta zama "bawan" Rasha".
Rasha ta ce tsarin Nord Stream 2, wanda zai kai dala biliyan 11, kuma zai ƙaru zuwa murabba'in mita biliyan 110 ta tsawonsa da kuma fadinsa, tsarin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Rasha ta ce Amirka ta ƙi wannan tsarin domin dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma ta ce wannan ƙiyayya ta nuna cewa ta yi amfani da tsarin kasuwanci da ya dace.
"Na yi imani cewa mun yarda cewa sayar da makamashi ba zai zama barazana ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani da makamashi su sami damar zaɓar wanda za su sayar da shi", in ji Ministan Harkokin Makamashi Aleksandr Novak a lokacin da ya gana da Ministan Harkokin Makamashi na Amirka, Rick Perry a birnin Moscow a watan Satumba.
Ba ta amince da matakin da Amirka ta ɗauka ba, kuma Jamus ta nace cewa za ta ci gaba da bin wannan tsarin.
Ƙungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus ta yi kira ga Amirka ta ƙi shiga yarjejeniyar samar da makamashi da kuma haɗin gwiwar Jamus da Rasha.
"Ina baƙin ciki sosai idan wani ƙasa ya shiga cikin sayenmu na iko", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban BDI bayan taron shugaban Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren Za Ta Yi "Tunanin" Taimakon Ta a Zaben Shugaban Kasa na 2020, Wakilin Massachusetts Ya Bayyana
A ranar Asabar, Elizabeth Warren, wakilin Massachusetts ta ce za ta yi "tunani sosai" game da yin zaɓen shugaban ƙasa bayan zaɓen tsakiyar.
A wani taro da aka yi a birnin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi la'akari da yadda zai yi hakan.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da "mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya haɗa da wata mace mai daraja", in ji The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, suna son su "yi tunani sosai" game da batun shiga zaben shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump a taron, yana cewa "yana kai yankin zuwa wani bangare da bai dace ba.
"Ina damuwa sosai game da abin da Donald Trump yake yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
Warren ya jagoranci zanga-zangar da aka yi wa Trump da Brett Kavanaugh da aka nada a Kotun Koli.
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "hakika muna bukatar FBI ta bincika mu kafin mu yi zabe".
Gwamnatin da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis, ta nuna cewa yawancin mazauna yankin Warren ba su tsammanin ya dace su tsaya takara a zaben 2020.
Kashi 98 cikin 100 na "masu-yin zabe" a Massachusetts sun ce wannan sanatan bai kamata ya yi aiki ba, in ji Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe.
Kashi 32 cikin 100 sun amince da wannan shawarar.
Binciken ya nuna cewa yawancin mutane sun amince da cewa tsohon gwamnan Deval Patrick ya kamata ya shiga, yayin da kashi 38 cikin 100 ke goyon bayan wannan yiwuwar kuma kashi 48 cikin 100 suna adawa.
Wasu daga cikin sanannun 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da ake zargi da kasancewa cikin 2020 sun hada da mataimakin shugaban kasar Joe Biden da Sanata na Vermont Bernie Sanders.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara mai kyau a watan Janairu, in ji Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta tattauna batun PTSD da Track Palin a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya yi shekara guda a Iraki bayan an rubuta shi a watan Satumba.
An kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da aikata mugunta a gida a daren Litinin
"Ta hanyar abin da ɗana ya fuskanta, ta hanyar dawowa, na fahimci wasu iyalai da ke fama da PTSD da kuma wasu daga cikin abubuwan da sojojinmu ke fuskanta", in ji shi ga masu sauraro a taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta ce kamawarta "babban abu ne da babu wanda yake so ya yi magana a kai" kuma game da ɗanta da wasu 'yan yaƙi, "sun dawo da ɗan gajiya, sun dawo da ƙarfi, sun dawo suna mamakin ko akwai daraja ga abin da abokan aikinta da ma'aikatanta, da kuma kowane ɗan soja, suka ba wa wannan ƙasa".
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a birnin Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafin wata mata, da hana rahoton wani laifi na cin zarafin iyali da kuma mallakar makami a lokacin da yake shan giya, in ji Dan Bennett, Kakakin Sashen 'Yan Sanda na birnin Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da kuma D.C. sun yi ta hamayya da sabon dokar da ta kāre 'yan gudun hijira
Jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar Columbia sun yi hamayya da sabuwar dokar da ta hana samun taimako ga waɗanda suka gudu daga 'yan ta'adda da kuma tashin hankali a gida.
Lauyoyi daga jihohi 18 da jihohi sun shigar da kara a kotun Washington a ranar Juma'a don tallafawa wani ɗan gudun hijira mai neman kariyar da kuma adawa da dokar, a cewar rahoton NBC News.
Ba a bayyana sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. da Kungiyar 'Yancin Bil Adama ta Amirka ta shigar a watan Agusta a kan manufofin gwamnati ba.
Ta ce mijinta "da kuma 'ya'yanta masu zalunci", suna tsananta mata amma hukumomin Amirka sun ƙi ta nemi mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare shi a Texas.
Lauyoyin da ke ba da taimako ga Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke kawo yawan masu neman mafaka zuwa Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fuskantar ƙaruwar matsalolin da ake fuskanta saboda ƙungiyoyin tashin hankali da tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabon dokar Amurka kan kare 'yan gudun hijira daga barazanar ta sauya hukuncin 2014 na Hukumar Kula da Daukaka kara ta Baƙi wanda ke ba da izinin baƙi marasa takaddun don tserewa daga tashin hankali na gida don neman kariya.
