A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya sake aukuwa a yammacin Donggala, ya kashe mutane tara.
A yankin Pacific, Indonesia tana da girgizar ƙasa da yawa.
Ga jerin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya-bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afku a yammacin yankin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su mutanen Aceh ne.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da kuma farkon Afrilu, girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta addabi gabar yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudu da tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya yi wa tsibirin kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa Padang, babban birnin yankin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani ƙaramin girgizar ƙasa ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ya jawo lalacewa da tsoro domin an tuna wa mutane da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka kashe mutane da yawa a shekara ta 2004.
Babu tsunami da ya faru a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da ɗari sun mutu a sakamakon fashewar gidaje.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afka wa tsibirin Lombok, babban tsibirin baƙi na ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
