Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia: an kashe ɗaruruwan mutane
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a tsibirin Sulawesi a ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Jumma'a
