'Yan kotun suna neman a yanke wa waɗanda ake zargi da aikata ta'addanci hukuncin kisa
Alƙalai a Birnin New York suna son a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, a cikin abin da ake tuhumarsa da aikata ta'addanci a birnin NYC da kuma kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da kotun jihar ba ta yanke ba tun 1953.
An ce Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya a Home Depot don yin ta'addanci a kan hanyar keke kusa da babbar hanyar West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, yana kashe masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke a kan titi a watan Oktoba.
Don a tabbatar da cewa hukuncin kisa ya cancanci, alƙalai suna bukatar su ba da shaida cewa Saipov "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas kuma "da gangan" ya yi wa wasu lahani, bisa ga dokar da ta shafi neman wannan hukuncin, da aka bayar a Kudancin Jihar New York.
A duk waɗannan shari'o'in, ana yanke hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda aka ambata a cikin takardar kotu.
Bayan makonni da yawa, babban kotun ya yanke hukuncin cewa Saipov yana da laifuffuka 22, ciki har da laifuffuka takwas na kisan kai da ake yi da yaudara, da kuma laifuffuka na aikata laifi da lalata mota.
Alƙalai sun ce an "shirya shari'ar da kyau kuma an yi la'akari da ita sosai", suna kwatanta yadda Saipov ya yi "ainihin laifi, mai tsanani da kuma mummunan hali".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya sa wasu suka ji rauni, kuma ya sa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco baƙin ciki", a cikin takardar da aka yi game da hukuncin.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe su baƙi ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shige da kotun Kudancin New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa.
An samu wanda aka tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe 'yan kasuwa biyu da ke sayar da ƙwayoyi, amma a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009, an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a kurkuku.
A shekara ta 1953, an yanke wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a birnin New York.
An kashe ma'aurata na iyalin Rosenberg a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, ɗan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin damuwa game da abin da ya yi a cikin kwanaki da watanni masu zuwa, a cewar takardun kotu.
Sun gaya wa masu binciken cewa sun ji daɗin abin da suka yi, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Saipov ya shaidawa jami'an gwamnati cewa an bukaci shi ya yi hakan bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, bisa ga bayanan da ake bayarwa game da shari'arsa.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitinsa, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Ya ƙi zargin da aka yi masa na 22.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin wakilan Saipov, ya ce "ya yi baƙin ciki" game da shawarar da alƙalan jihar suka yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar bukatar da ake yi na kasancewa a kurkuku kuma ba a bar shi ba zai ƙara baƙin ciki ga duk wanda aka shafa", in ji Patton.
Lauyoyin Saipov sun riga sun roƙi alƙalai su hana su yanke hukuncin kisa.
