Syria "ta shirya" don 'yan gudun hijira su koma, in ji Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen
Syria ta ce tana shirye ta dawo da 'yan gudun hijira kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina ƙasar da ta yi shekaru bakwai tana fama da yaƙi.
Da yake jawabi a Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce abubuwa suna ci gaba a ƙasar.
"Yanzu mun sami kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali saboda ci gaba da yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi
Gwamnati tana ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don ta mai da al'adunsu.
A yanzu, an kafa tsarin da ya dace don 'yan gudun hijira su koma ƙasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma yanayin tattalin arziki da ya shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma ɗabi'arsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan kasar Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suka rage a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta amince da taimakon da ake ba ta don ta sake gina ƙasar.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai iya karɓar taimako da wasu buƙatu ko taimako daga ƙasashen da suka tallafa wa 'yan ta'adda ba.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar golf ta Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 bayan ta doke Amurka da maki 16 da rabi daga 10 da rabi a filin wasa na Le Gold National, a waje da birnin Paris, Faransa.
Ƙasar Amirka ta ci gasar Ryder Cup a shekara shida a jere a gasar Turai, kuma ba ta taɓa lashe gasar ba tun shekara ta 1993.
Ƙungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai da ta yi nasara a kan tawagar Amirka ta ci kwallaye 14.5 kuma ta ci gasar a karo na biyu.
Phil Mickelson, dan wasan Amurka, wanda ya ƙi nuna ƙarfinsa a gasar, ya jefa ƙwallon a cikin wani rami marar kyau wanda ya ba abokin hamayyarsa Francesco Molinari damar cin nasara.
'Yan wasan Italiya sun yi wasan da ya fi kyau a duk sassan gasar, kuma hakan ya sa ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan 4 da suka ci 5-0-0 a gasar a shekara ta 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth bai yi sanyin gwiwa ba yayin da ya yi rashin nasara da maki 5 da 4 a kan dan wasan Turai Thorbjorn Olesen daga Denmark, wanda bai samu nasara ba.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowa shahara a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya fadi 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda wataƙila ya buga wasan karshe a gasar cin kofin Ryder ta duniya.
Dan wasan Ryder Cup, Spaniard Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara tare da maki 25.5 a lokacin wasan.
"Ba na kuka ba amma har yau ba zan iya yin kome ba.
Wannan shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga malaminmu Thomas don ya yi mini baftisma da kuma amincewa da ni.
Ina farin ciki sosai cewa na sake samun ƙoƙon.
Manufar ita ce tawagarmu ta yi nasara, kuma ina farin cikin kasancewa cikin wannan nasara", in ji Garcia, wanda ya yi farin ciki sosai bayan nasarar tawagarsa ta Turai.
Ya gode wa dan kasarsa John Ram wanda ya ci Amurka Tiger Woods 2&1 a wasan daya-da-daya a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Ina alfahari da na ci Tiger Woods, wanda ya yi nasara sosai sa'ad da na girma ina kallon shi yana wasa.
Woods ya ci nasara a wasanni hudu a Faransa kuma a yanzu ya samu nasara a gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup da ta kai 13-21-3.
Wannan abin mamaki ne idan aka yi la'akari da cewa wannan mutum ne mafi girma a duniya, wanda ya lashe wasanni 14 kuma Jack Nicklaus ne kaɗai ya fi shi.
Ƙungiyar USA ta yi aiki tukuru a ƙarshen mako don samun sakamako mai kyau ban da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka buga golf mafi girma a duk wasanni.
Babban jami'in Amurka Jim Furyk ya yi magana bayan ya buga wasan da ya sa ya yi wa tawagarsa takaici, "Ina alfahari da waɗannan samarin, sun yi aiki tuƙuru.
A wannan safiya mun yi wa tawagar Turai barazana.
Yaƙin ya kasance da wuya.
Duk girmamawa ta tabbata ga Thomas.
Yana da kyau.
Dukkan 'yan wasan 12 sun yi nasara sosai.
Idan muka yi wasu abubuwa, zan iya aiki tare da PGA na Amirka da kuma Kwamitin Ryder Cup kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan abokaina 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa shugabansu.
Ka yi farin ciki.
Bari mu yarda cewa abokanmu sun yi wasa da kyau fiye da mu".
